  "original_title": "\u0dbd\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dda \u0d85\u0dbb\u0dca\u0db6\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dba \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc3\u0db3\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0d85\u0db1\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dca \u0dab\u0dba \u0dc4\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dd2\u0dba\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0db8\u0d9c \u0dc3\u0db8\u0dca\u0db6\u0db1\u0dca\u0db0\u0dd3\u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dab\u0dba \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0db1\u0dc0\u0dcf - \u0da2\u0db4\u0dcf\u0db1\u0dba",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Coordinating with other creditors to resolve Sri Lanka's crisis - Japan",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "TOKYO, Aug 30 (Reuters) - Japan will coordinate with other creditors to resolve Sri Lanka's financial crisis and urge all creditor nations to discuss Sri Lanka's debt from the same table, Japanese Finance Minister Shunichi Suzuki said on Tuesday.",
        "\"We are concerned about the dire socio-economic situation in Sri Lanka,\" Mr Suziki told reporters.",
        "He said that talks with the International Monetary Fund (IMF) should be expedited to implement a debt relief package for Sri Lanka and all bilateral creditors including China and India should meet to discuss the issue.",
        "\"Japan wants to actively cooperate with other lending countries and public organizations.\" He said."
      ],
